# Contributing to Insightfy

- [Contributing to Insighty](#contributing-to-the-monitoring-as-code-tool)
  - [What to contribute](#what-to-contribute)
  - [How to contribute](#how-to-contribute)

## What to contribute

This tool was created out of the following use cases but not limited to:

* Provide an easy way to generate key business impacting metrics leveraging on Dynatrace APIs
    - License Metrics
    - Feature Flags
    - Problem Analysis
    - Incident Metrics

* Create Customized Benefits Valuation/Dashboard Reports based on above metrics
* Dashboard Reports
* Single Value Trends
* Setting Custom Alerts
* Compare consumption or adoption metrics across different endpoints

## How to contribute

You are welcome to contribute to Insightfy.
Use issues for discussing proposals or to raise a question.
If you have improvements to Dynatrace Operator, please submit your pull request.
For those just getting started, consult this  [guide](https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request-from-a-fork/).
